         <abstract id="aspace_57856e70d1ebe8b66cd7edd8606c2c3f">The records consist of correspondence, reports, minutes, drawings, and subscription lists documenting the activities of Yale committees, such as the Lecture Committee, Committee on University Publications, Committee on Memorials, and the Committee on Faculty Appointments.</abstract>
    
      </did>
      <odd id="aspace_a60a5f8bd389d3e2d6b0c9c077db50b9">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 6 (YRG 6), Records of Yale committees.</p>  
      </odd>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_3aefc5399f750670ded462d800030942">
         <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
