      <prefercite id="aspace_3b9a3966368347a8fb1ec6c1a535352a">
         <head>Preferred Citation</head>
         <p>Committees of Yale University Records (RU 153). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.</p>  
      </prefercite>
      <arrangement id="aspace_099b5c0b2f74ffb1eb1aa03b7ca57efa">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The records are arranged by accession.</p>  
      </arrangement>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_c9e43991f69ff93c357b3a59cdf05dba">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of correspondence, reports, minutes, drawings, and subscription lists documenting the activities of Yale committees, such as the Lecture Committee, Committee on University Publications, Committee on Memorials, and the Committee on Faculty Appointments.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
